                    <h3>How do instant payouts work for walkers?</h3>
                    <p>Walkers receive payments directly to their bank account within 24 hours of completing a walk. No waiting for weekly or monthly payouts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Are there really no fees for dog owners?</h3>
                    <p>Yes! Dog owners can book walks completely free. We charge walkers a flat monthly subscription instead of taking a percentage of their earnings.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What happens if I need to cancel?</h3>
                    <p>You can cancel your subscription at any time from your profile settings. You'll retain access until the end of your billing period.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Is my dog insured during walks?</h3>
